node.text: When you're on serious a pitch, you have to get into a serious mindset, Jerry. The Send Portal doesn't mess around. It doesn't care who you are; if you're "important" at your day job or you're a "good" parent at home. It'll suck you in. It'll spit you out. It'll change how you look at future sends #EnterTheSendPortal // @mellew_
